## Step Completion

When ALL substeps above are completed:
1. Call `save_step_report(step_name="{{ step.id }}", status="completed", ...)`
2. Call `write_todo(step_id="{{ step.id }}", status="completed")` to advance to the next step
{% if next_step %}
3. Call `write_todo(step_id="{{ next_step.id }}", status="in_progress")` to start {{ next_step.id }} ({{ next_step.name }})
{% endif %}

⚠️ You MUST call write_todo to advance — do NOT produce a text-only response.
